				<title>Size Problem</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9331832/scp-3286#post-4133730</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 28 Jan 2019 17:44:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Deadly Bread</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3988532</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The size is supposed to be the way it is. The Foundation is releasing the fish in the Containment Procedures to feed the colony of 3286. They make sure the fish is bigger than 44&#160;cm so that they can’t use it in the creation ritual.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
