				<wikidot:authorName>Mike44njdevils</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4352511</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like this concept, though it seems a little &quot;eh&quot;. Maybe experiment(s) to communicate (producing a tone similar to the one used in the -B ritual)?</p> <p>Also a note: in the special containment procedures, the fish released is noted to be GREATER than 45cm. In the description, you changed it to LESS than 45cm.</p> <p>Null vote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
